I"o<h2 id="tor">Tor</h2>
<p>Add those lines to <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/tor/torrc</code>:</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Transport 9040
DNSPort 5353
</code></pre></div></div>

